/// @name moz
/// @author Tyler Benton
/// @page helpers/mixins
/// @description This allows you to write specific styles for mozilla firefox only
/// @markup {styl} **Example:**
/// +moz() {
///   // removes the weird styling in firefox
///   -moz-appearance: none;
///   text-indent: 0.01px;
///   text-overflow: '';
/// }
moz()
  @-moz-document url-prefix()
    /{selector()}
      {block}